{"type": "article", "id": 52115, "title": "PUMA 卖得不错，以及，最近流行的 Tiny sunglasses 似曾相识 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-04-13T03:43:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 32, "name": "时尚"}, {"id": 9111, "name": "公司"}, {"id": 1690, "name": "流行"}, {"id": 44164, "name": "Puma"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 27474, "name": "Glossier"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 1303675, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 67, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180413113401pTOCtXSYEkIb4MU7.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\"><b>一些重要的新闻：</b></h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/retail/glossier-opening-permanent-store-los-angeles-melrose-avenue-1202647687/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美妆品牌 Glossier 又开了一家实体店</b></a> | 原线上美妆品牌 Glossier 近日在 L.A 开了一家永久门店，这是品牌继纽约开店后在线下设立的第二家实体店。Glossier 创始人 Emily Weiss 透露，LA 对 Glossier 来说是需求量很大的市场，并且品牌的快闪店和纽约店客流量大，而且转化率达 50%，这意味有一半入店的顾客在店内消费过。另外，门店的设计灵感取材于当地文化，LA 新店将会布置一个“ Glossier 峡谷”，意在为年轻顾客制造出自拍环境。<br></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/puma-q1-sales-1202648143/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Puma 官方称第一季度业绩增长</b></a> | 根据初步数据结果显示，运动品牌 Puma 本财年第一季度销售额上涨 12% 至 11.3 亿欧元，虽然年初业绩有所增长，但 Puma 对此表示，在近期的市场环境中仍有不确定因素，包括波动的货币、不稳定的政治环境以及中美两国的贸易战。<br></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/bernard-arnault-rumors-lvmh-bid-chanel-fake-news-1202648156/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>奢侈品巨头 LVMH 否认收购 Chanel</b></a> | 本周三，LVMH 总裁 Bernard Arnault 在集团年度会议上否认收购 Chanel 的传闻，并表示虽然 Chanel 是很出色的公司，但集团不会与其有挂钩。另一方 Chanel 也同样反驳了这一假消息，称品牌不会出售。</p><h3><b>一些值得一看的：</b></h3><p><b>DIOR HOMME 推出了 2018 秋季GOLD CAPSULE系列</b>，<a name=\"_Hlk510460564\"></a>以美轮美奂的金色元素致敬迪奥经典。</p><p class=\"\">该系列将于 4 月公开发售，其中三款是中国独家限定产品：黑色尼龙背包饰以金色小蜜蜂与 DIOR 标识，金色小蜜蜂镂空金属挂饰及白色胶底小牛皮运动鞋饰以金色小蜜蜂烫金图案。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413122326oRKP58AY4qviXOgJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">photo: Dior</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413122325BeNDaiYpw0LTbIFR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">photo: Dior</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413122327MsRcmKhUkQbJadZi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500938\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">photo: Dior</figcaption></figure></div><p>在今年的“<a href=\"https://www.ikea.com/gb/en/ikea/ikea-art-event-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><b>宜家艺术节</b></a>（IKEA Art Event）”上，宜家以“玩具艺术和瑞典玻璃艺术”为主题，邀请了来自世界各地的 8 位艺术家来设计制作趣味十足的玻璃雕像。其中有来自香港艺术家 Michael Lau 设计的“灵魂玩具（Soul Toy）”的雕像，也有澳大利亚艺术家和玩具设计师 Nathan Jurevicius 设计的猫头鹰。<br></p><p class=\"\">宜家艺术节创意主管 Henrik Mos 对此表示想看看古老的传统与新兴的艺术形式结合在一起会发生什么，“我认为，我们发现了某些极富趣味的元素，有望将玻璃艺术推向一个新的时代。”<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413102719itVDNn5qOmYGK7a4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>Photo: IKEA</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413102732ptRTsZwOhVx4Mbe5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: IKEA</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413102733iaY40o1phqMNBP8R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: IKEA</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413102737npskmoTXAQ8ayH9N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: IKEA</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413102741Tnc5o3RJ2FzkPXqM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: IKEA</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://fashionista.com/2018/04/alexander-wang-adidas-originals-collection-season-three-drop-one\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alexander Wang 与 Adidas Originals的第三季合作系列发布</a></b>，此次 Alenander Wang 从工厂制造过程中的产生误差和缺陷汲取灵感，将这些不足转换为像素化图案、不规则印花以及层压起皱纹路等设计元素贯穿在系列始终。<br></p><p class=\"\">该系列产品将于 4 月 21 号在官方网店和线下指定门店发售。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413103329pP5RS23qbaWfTCjU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: Adidas Originals</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413103329dtaMC41oXpkS59Aq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: Adidas Originals</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413103346icO6oXQvszhJm9Hu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: Adidas Originals</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413103345yGxPsK31zQH9JDcl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: Adidas Originals</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413103346ow3CFsWhuU0y8rJg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: Adidas Originals</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413103346jLXfSoWEvwptnCVU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: Adidas Originals</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413103345DPzY41Emuf06Vlwg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: Adidas Originals</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">从 Kendall Jenner、Bella Hadid 等网红超模到上海时装周街头，<b>Tiny Sunglasses 似乎是今年时尚圈的大势</b>。实际上，与其说是流行，不如说是致敬，因为Tiny Sunglasses 这一流行单品的灵感大多是来源于 90 年代动作电影里的人物造型。</p><p class=\"\">近日，<a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/tiny-sunglasses-trend-movies/\" rel=\"nofollow\">潮流网站 highsnobiety</a> 就总结了 20 部最佳 Tiny sunglasses 造型的老电影，在这里我们提取了几部最标志性的影片。</p><p class=\"\">1、黑客帝国-1999</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413111210ha0q52HJdY7g4UV1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.307407\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: douban</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413111209lVPKx0dfinsyXu3p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.475000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: douban</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413111209CQ0vsuV4F9JhfG1B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.509259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: douban</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">2、这个杀手不太冷-1994</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413111755r7WUNgX0MqLVofh6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.489362\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: douban</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413111806URl4rDpLuqP6HOXc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: douban</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413111806v3faYosRn9z8A6d1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: douban</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">3、修女也疯狂2-1993<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413112053diLAbfmJwUW7y8S0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.477833\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: douban</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413112053zkrXsqH5bQ9ETwx0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562963\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: douban</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">4、天生杀人狂-1994</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413112701mzULr8ZMghy9IPsE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.443503\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: douban</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413112700Ux0mMtDAyG7B31fh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.661111\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: douban</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180413112754hQFx90ypcv2YNdUb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: douban</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来源：puma</p>"}